reviewText: Janich always does a good job diagramming what he is demonstrating. Safe media DVD are high quality and the best self defense on the market right now.
I found it met my expectations and provided a usable and practical practice guide to improve improve and maintain skills.

I'd give this 5 stars, but I have seen other works by this author that I consider better presented. Think what you will, being prepared, in any amount, is a whole lot better than the alternative. This entire DVD contains useful, carefully explained, and needed information for this day and age. Again, an ounce of self preservation is a whole lot better than the alternative.
This is a super poor production but Mr. Janich clearly knows his stuff.  I did learn several new opening techniques so I'd say it was worth it.
